short.th: คุณต้องได้รับคะแนนสูงสุดด้วยรถของคุณโดยไม่ต้องชนสิ่งกีดขวางในอุโมงค์

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Start an endless adventure with a stylized car! Pass the obstacles and start the fun adventure. Car tunnel racing, among the car games, has a different concept. On an endless racing track, you must avoid thorn obstacles, pass by them, and continue. Since the track is bumpy, it would be the right choice to steer your vehicle according to the obstacles in front of you in the car racing game.

How To Play
You can move your 4x4 vehicle on the track using arrow keys. Passing through the blue circles with your 4x4 SUV while progressing on the track provides you with additional points.

Car Tunnel Racing Game Features
✓ Infinity level
✓ 3D designer
✓ Easy control
✓ Cartoon car

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Car Tunnel Racing Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
